**who —** THE LANDS BETWEEN — the shattered Order and the long climb to the throne

**what —** Elden Ring — the Outer Gods and their elements, the Eternals who stand outside death and time, the demigod children of the Shattering, and a Tarnished climbing from nobody to Elden Lord.

**where —** the Lands Between, under the shattered Elden Ring and the golden Erdtree  Framework inputs: the Elden Ring; the Erdtree and grace; the Elementals; the Eternals  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0 · Universe David 0)

**why —** A god shattered the Order with her own hand; the graceless were called back to mend or remake it.

**how —** Crystallized from the game and its expansion — the Elementals, the Eternals, and the cast, sealed.

**◌ the mythos —** A god shattered the Order with her own hand; the graceless were called back to mend or remake it. Game of the Year 2022; the Shattering of the Ring is the wound the whole world inherits.

**the moniker —** ⟦THE LANDS BETWEEN:ER:98dce2⟧ · spoken *xum-braer-krys*

